Appliances























Get Details





10% – 25% OFF Select Appliance Special Values
Offer applies to select items only. Also not valid on: clearance items; Dacor, ICON, Fisher & Paykel, Monogram, Smeg or Liebherr brand appliances (some brands not available in all markets/stores); water heaters; room air conditioners; previous sales; or services. Price in cart reflects discount. Some items available via Special Order only. See store for details. Valid 7/20/17 – 8/2/17.
Next-Day Delivery for In-Store Purchases or Purchases Made Through Our Customer Care Call Centers: Next-day delivery may be available on any in-stock major appliance for in-store or Customer Care Call Center purchases only. Customer must purchase in-stock major appliance and request next-day delivery in store or with a Customer Care representative (1-877-505-4926) before 4 p.m. local time and be within 30 miles of store location for next-day delivery. Next-day service is subject to delivery availability and not available for Lowes.com orders. No deliveries on Thanksgiving or Christmas. Additional fees may apply. Additional fees may include, but are not limited to, ferries, tolls and trip permits. US only. See store for details.
Next-day messaging is provided for information purposes only. Need help with appliances? Call 1-877-391-5627 to speak with an appliance specialist.
Free Local Delivery: Free local delivery available for any major appliance $396 or more (calculated after applicable discounts, before taxes, installation, additional delivery and extended protection fees, if any). No deliveries on Thanksgiving or Christmas. Additional fees may apply. US only. See store for details.
♦30-day major appliance satisfaction guarantee based on Lowe’s refund and price match policies. For questions, please see your local store or call 1-800-445-6937.
*View our price match guarantee.
































































































































































