Shop Appliances With Lowe’s
Lowe’s has everything you need when it comes to home appliances, from the laundry room to the best kitchen appliances. Choose from our selection of trusted brands for ranges, ovens, dishwashers, refrigerators, freezers, washers, dryers, microwaves, small appliances, appliance parts, vacuums and more. When it comes to buying appliances, there are a ton of options. It’s all about finding the fridge, portable dishwasher, stove, oven, washer dryer combo or stackable washer dryer combo that best fits your home. Want a stainless steel refrigerator or washing machine? Try our appliance buying guides to help you compare a Samsung Refrigerator to a LG Refrigerator or Maytag Dishwasher to a Bosch Dishwasher. Looking for ENERGY STAR® qualified appliances or specific appliances? We’ve got you covered.


























