10% OFF All Shingles, Accessories and Labor When Installed Through Lowe’s
Discount applies to product and labor. Requires product and install through Lowe's and requires full roof replacement. Discount reflected in customer quote. Must schedule in-home consultation on or before 8/1/17 and purchase project on or before 8/4/17 to receive discount. In-store offer only. Install by independent contractors. See store associate for details and restrictions and Lowes.com/licensenumbers for licensure.
Installation services guaranteed by Lowe’s labor warranty and available through independent contractors, licensed and registered where applicable. License numbers and certifications held by or on behalf of Lowe’s Home Centers, LLC. See Lowes.com/licensing for current license numbers. Additional charges may apply for permit fees and for any product and service not included in basic installation. Non-refundable site assessment fee may be required, which is credited to final project price if project is purchased through Lowe’s. Install fees and additional charges based on total product recommended by installer’s assessment of your project site. Product recommendation includes waste and exceeds actual project square footage. All offers limited to single-family residences, may not be available in all areas and not valid on previous purchases. Minimum labor charges may apply.



















