10% Military Discount





Lowe's offers a 10% military discount to support the men and women who are currently serving our country in the Armed Services. More Info »  The 10% discount is also good for retired veterans and VA recipients as well as immediate family of those who are currently serving, retired veterans, or VA recipients. 5/1/17 Update: Lowe's expands support of the military by offering 10% off personal purchase everyday to current and honorably discharged members of the U.S. Armed Forces.

