Kobalt 46-Piece Standard and Metric Tool Set



$14.98
$39.98 (63% off)

✓Verified

Get a grip on any job with this Kobalt Interchangeable Drive 46-Piece Standard and Metric Mechanic's Tool Set on sale at Lowe's for $14.98. It features spline sockets, a ratchet handle, three extensions, and more. The spline sockets are designed to work 7 types of fasteners, including SAE and metric, 6-point, 12-point, star, square, and most rounded nuts and bolts. A similar set sells for $29.98 at Amazon.
More Info »


