$10 Off $50+ Purchase | Ends Soon





Many of Lowe's stores are offering a free $10 off $50 coupon if you shop in store or online now through January 18th. More Info »  View the printable coupon for a complete list of participating stores. I checked the stores in my area and nearly all of them were on the list! One-time-use coupon will be printed on your in-store receipt,or,for Lowes.com purchases, coupon willbe sent within 48 hours to customer email address provided at time of online checkout.

