www.lowes.com

How to Use Lowe's Coupons:Enter Lowe's coupon in the "Promotion Code" field on the shopping cart page under "Cart Summary". Click "Apply Code" to see discount amount deduced prior to checkout.Lowe's Tips & Tricks:Sign up for the email list to receive offers for Lowe'sCheck out the online rebates sectionCheck out their weekly ad online to see what is on sale each weekDownload the app to your smartphone for additional money saving opportunities Lowe's Shipping / Return Policy:Orders that are shipping to stores ship for free. If your order total is over $49, standard shipping will be free if it is delivering to within the continental United States. It must also weigh less than 150lbs. Returns may be made within 90 days of purchase. Certain items must be returned within 30 days of purchase. If you purchased a major appliance, Lowe's will replace it within 7 days of purchase if it has a manufacturing defect. Contact Lowe's:To contact Customer Care, you may call 1-800-445-6937. There is also a link online that you can click to email their team instead. Do not forget to check out their Help Center first, there are a ton of sections that may be able to answer your question first.

