Insulation Company | Concord
Founded in 1978 by Tom and Shelly McHale, McHale’s Environmental Insulation Co. is a leading insulation contractor serving Concord, Martinez, Pleasant Hill, Walnut Creek, Lafayette, Orinda, Oakland, Berkeley and surrounding areas of California. We use the latest technology to service both the residential and commercial market. Our goal is to provide not only quality service but quality material while exceeding client expectations. We’ve earned our reputation by listening to our clients needs while providing energy efficient insulation solutions. McHale’s Environmental Insulation Co. encourages you to contact us with any question you may have. 

Who We Are
We are your Bay Area home energy specialists, providing cellulose, fiberglass, cotton and radiant barrier insulation for attics, walls and floors. We have been helping homeowners and businesses reduce their energy bills for over three decades, serving over 70,000 customers. For more information about our team at McHale’s Environmental Insulation Co. please visit our About Page and let us save you money while increasing your comfort. 

Did You Know?
The U.S. Department of Energy states that homeowners may be able to reduce their energy bills from 10% to 35% by increasing the amount of insulation in their homes. 

